      "text": [
        " أَبُو اَلْحَسَنِ اَلْأَوَّلُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «قِيلُوا فَإِنَّ اَللَّهَ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ يُطْعِمُ اَلصَّائِمَ وَ يَسْقِيهِ فِي مَنَامِهِ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1782 - Abu al-Hasan al-Awwal (as) said:\n\"Take a nap, for Allah (swt), the Almighty, feeds and gives drink to the fasting person while they sleep.\""
        ]
      }
    },
